{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "8a22eed4-1972-4fb8-8464-62aff0553f1d",
    "name": "Interact with Stained Glass Window",
    "sceneId": "d43bff20-2b5d-497c-b175-e3ca71ebcd95",
    "propId": "c2ee935c-1bdf-4d7b-b0e9-86b5841abf14",
    "actorId": null,
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.interact",
        "name": "Interact"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "56783168-b756-4bbc-9265-aa02e33df0f5",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "64d96818-3495-422f-ace4-e8ca153f6215",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1a0bf8c0-f104-4eff-a63f-523d0aa315ab",
                            "text": "Look at the Stained Glass",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6222a8f6-4123-4f4b-8fae-b5f59c41e27d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "It's beautiful. A Knight of the Luminar. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6eceea98-2d67-4756-8535-c9e154839457",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "There's an inscription: \"For all those who have dedicated their lives to bring the light to drive away the darkness.\" \n",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "28b2a589-7ff1-4ffa-bf17-bbbf88546e0f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Maybe somebody will do a stained glass version of <i>me</i> when <i>I'm</i> history.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "091e90c8-9c0d-4680-8d6c-5bb647fe3914",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I'll probably be lucky to get a <i>stained glass</i>. I mean, an actual stained glass, like from the kitchen.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "aea0c0c1-b2b0-4a08-aea2-870ceb44a429",
                            "text": "Take the Stained Glass",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "83743a8d-51fe-4d16-b762-37869c4200e9",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Hmm... it's cemented in very professionally.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7c8ce552-4f63-4884-a314-516f245850e6",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Stealing it would be a big job. I don't really have the time. Or the tools. Or the know-how. Other than that...",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "932f3365-a9c3-4c1c-b46b-ae51b3d5df2f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "And, all things considered, I'd rather not burn in the fiery pits of hell for all eternity.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                                    "id": "da3c3023-11ad-4544-bf78-ffcac299dc10",
                                    "scope": "target",
                                    "scopeId": "c2ee935c-1bdf-4d7b-b0e9-86b5841abf14",
                                    "scopeFilterId": "d43bff20-2b5d-497c-b175-e3ca71ebcd95",
                                    "tagsToAdd": "TakenOnce",
                                    "tagsToRemove": null
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1eca1c8b-d11e-46c7-9a6c-8e74a46da63b",
                            "text": "Break the Stained Glass",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                "scope": "target",
                                                "scopeId": null,
                                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                                "tags": "TakenOnce",
                                                "has": false
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "40c0f2a1-cd4b-4f45-b8a7-920f2dcb4186",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "Breaking this would certainly be a Richard move.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "57eef817-679f-4128-a021-b5514dc815a6",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Richard was a neighborhood bully who couldn't resist breaking church windows, picking on little kids, pulling mean pranks, stuff like that. ",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "078dfb6b-ce0c-4a43-88f5-dcb4ba949f1e",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "He thought he was a rebel. But he was really just a big Richard. I don't know any other word to describe him.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "cf5aa11c-9551-4e3a-b47e-504158e317bd",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "I've already made it clear that I don't want to burn in the fiery pits of hell. ",
                                                    "emotion": "3",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "408c025f-592b-42ab-b0b0-72bfe8fa13a9",
                            "text": "Sense Magic",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "e9fba320-402a-4927-b694-cad5fe2602f0",
                                    "scriptId": "b1c2ecc1-eb00-49ed-a7ba-ea6af625c355",
                                    "entryPointId": "56783168-b756-4bbc-9265-aa02e33df0f5",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "5f4c53b2-540d-4627-af71-7ede35c6d84b",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "85c67567-c9e4-4c3b-aaf1-ed02964749ce",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "There's magic here that lights up the glass so that it shines. There's also a spell to affect emotions. I can feel hope and inspiration just looking at it.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "actor",
                                "scopeId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "SenseMagic",
                                "has": true
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": true,
                    "Unique": false
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}